*Njihovim* trudom su postigli uspeh. (They achieved success through their hard work.)

*Njihovim* idejama su obogatile život. (Their ideas enriched life.)

Njihovo* ponašanje je obeležilo događaj. (Their behavior marked the event.)

Njihovo* hrabro činjenje je bilo pohvaljeno. (Their brave deed was praised.)

*Njihovim* naporima su zaradili nagrade. (They earned rewards by their efforts.)